          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Broadband Buildout Accountability Act</strong></p> <p>This bill makes actions or decisions of the National Telecommunications and Information Administration concerning the Broadband Equity, Access, and Deployment Program subject to the Freedom of Information Act, which governs the release of federal documents.</p>]]>
        </text>
